Service Details: Offers a variety of recreational, dance and physical fitness programs for children and youth such as Family Day Fun & Fitness Frenzy!; Craft 'n' Swim; Science 'n' Swim; Try Hip Hop and Pre-teen Hip Hop; Weekend Boredom Busters; Sweat 'n' Swim; Home Alone and Prepared; Girl Power; Guy Stuff; Active Kids Camp and Jr. Active Kids Camp; Spring Break Fun Camps; Fuel Your Fun; Movie 'n' Swim Night; Pro-D Day Camp; Kinder Gym; Toy Story; Babysitter Training Course; Junior and Youth Leaders in Training; as well as drop-in programs and pre-registration classes
